            <div class="title">
                Libyan Battle And Bombing Of Germany
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1942-06-02/debates/fbd22fc7-ffa3-4206-9602-582580eb9295/BilstonCorporationBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
