<p class="">With reference to the illuminating statement made by the Prime Minister, can he say whether that was a special report called for from General Auchinleck by the right hon. Gentleman in addition to the ordinary communiques, and when that information was received?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
